          ! SUBROUTINE INFORMATION:
          !    AUTHOR         Jason Glazer of GARD Analytics, Inc.
          !    DATE WRITTEN   January 2005
          !    MODIFIED       December 2008 to add Packaged VAV
          !    RE-ENGINEERED  na

          ! PURPOSE OF THIS SUBROUTINE:
